---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Jack Blondin | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Jack Blondin, Assistant at Heidi Blondin Financial. Leading digital innovation, website management, and social media strategy since 2019."
>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 items-start">

        <div class="md:col-span-1">
          <img
            src="/team/jack-portrait.jpg"
            alt="Jack Blondin — Assistant, Heidi Blondin Financial"
            class="w-full aspect-square object-cover object-top"
          />
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-serif text-xl text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Jack Blondin</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mt-1">Assistant</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-5">
            <p>Since 2019, Jack Blondin has played a key role in shaping the digital foundation of Heidi Blondin Financial. His expertise in website management, social media strategy, and office technology has been instrumental in driving innovation and supporting the firm's continued growth.</p>
            <p>Now working with the team full-time, Jack has led the transition toward a paperless environment and continues to enhance our digital tools and workflows. His forward-thinking approach and commitment to efficiency help ensure our operations remain modern and client-focused. Jack is also actively pursuing professional certifications to deepen his knowledge further and expand his impact.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="/heidi/" class="font-sans text-sm font-medium text-brand-gold underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-amber-700">← Back to the team</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <img
          src="/team/jack-family.jpg"
          alt="Jack Blondin with family"
          class="w-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
